body:

* [**Aneuploidy can be an evolutionary detour on the path to genetic adaptation**](https://mega.nz/file/hZ5jBbpQ#ieWt1sgkzi-j5o5LA4jISpoF5kxIyZpPdAVi33ruHAE) - invited speaker, *Gordon Research Conference on Molecular Mechanisms in Evolution*, Stonehill College, MA, July 2023 

* [**Self-Replicating Artificial Neural Networks Give Rise to Universal Evolutionary Dynamics**](https://mega.nz/file/ME4hVB4C#TwEgFTWjwRX3wQsIU49m15YTMhx8uZ6A5PDUwEvBjuM) - invited speaker, *Israeli Society for Evolutionary Biology*, Weizmann Institute, Israel, March 2022

* **Inferring the effective start dates of non-pharmaceutical interventions during COVID-19 outbreaks** [<i class="fa fa-youtube-play" aria-hidden="true"></i>](https://youtu.be/RVb_iOFSAbI) - invited speaker, *1st Meeting of the Center of Combating Pandemics*, Tel Aviv University, Israel, March 2022

* **The apple *sometimes* falls far from the tree: Evolution of non-vertical cultural transmission** - invited speaker, *The Language of Evolution & Evolution of Language* conference, Weizmann Institute, Israel, February 2020.

* [**Necessity is the mother of invention**](https://speakerdeck.com/yoavram/necessity-is-the-mother-of-invention) [<i class="fa fa-youtube-play" aria-hidden="true"></i>](https://youtu.be/JdG65hKqRW0) - invited speaker at the *TAU Theory-Fest* Evolution workshop, Tel Aviv University, Israel, January 2020.

* **Evolution of non-vertical transmission** [<i class="fa fa-youtube-play" aria-hidden="true"></i>](https://youtu.be/Q1OVdnunMP8?t=2756) - invited speaker at the *Socio-Technological Evolution of the Human Species* workshop, Safed, Israel, September 2019.

* **The role of aneuploidy in adaptive evolution** - oral presentation at the Gordon Research Conference on *Molecular Mechanisms in Evolution*, Stonehill College, Easton, MA, USA, June 2019.

* **Aneuploidy and adaptation in yeast and fungi** - oral presentation at Israel Society for Microbiology Annual Meeting, March 2019.

* [**Better to Learn from Whom? Evolution of non-vertical transmission**](https://www.dropbox.com/s/fwcv5cauiszeezd/retreat_2018.pdf?dl=0) - presentation at the IDC School of Computer Science annual retreat, June 2018.

* [**Evolution of non-vertical transmission in changing environments**](https://speakerdeck.com/yoavram/evolution-of-non-vertical-inheritance-in-changing-environments#) - special guest seminar at the Department of Molecular Genetics, Weizmann Institute of Science, January, 2018.

* [**Evolution on empirical adaptive landscapes**](https://speakerdeck.com/yoavram/evolution-on-empirical-adaptive-landscapes) - oral presentation at Israel Society for Microbiology Annual Meeting, April 2017.

* [**Predicting competition dynamics from growth curve data**](https://github.com/yoavram/ILANIT2017) - oral presentation at FISEB/ILANIT, Eilat, February 2017.

*   [**Evolution and Mutation During Stress**](https://github.com/yoavram/Reunion2016/raw/master/presentation.pdf) - Hebrew presentation.

*   [**How to Study Evolution using Scientific Python**](http://il.pycon.org/2016/about/speakers.html#61aa36d93e7cee64) [<i class="fa fa-youtube-play" aria-hidden="true"></i>](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2w8Tv016Frw) - oral presentation at the first *PyCon Israel* 2016, Tel-Aviv, Israel, May 2 - 3, 2016.

*   **Predicting competitions & estimating selection in microorganisms** - oral presentation at the Gordon Research Conference on *Biological Mechanisms in Evolution*, Stonehill College, Easton, MA, USA, June 28 - July 3, 2015.

*   **Stress-induced mutagenesis & complex adaptation** - poster at the *Forecasting Evolution?* conference in Lisbon, Portugal, July 8 - 11, 2015.

*   [**Stress-induced mutagenesis & complex adaptation**](https://speakerdeck.com/yoavram/stress-induced-mutagenesis-and-complex-adaptation) - short oral presentation at the Two2Many Systems Biology Conference, Weizmann Institute, March, 2015.

*   [**Adaptedness, Adaptability and Stress-Induced Mutagenesis**](https://github.com/yoavram/ESEB2013/raw/master/poster.pdf) - poster at ESEB 2013 in Lisbon, Portugal, August 19-24, 2013.

*   [**Stress-induced Mutagenesis and the Evolution of Complex Traits**](https://github.com/yoavram/GRC2013/blob/master/poster.pdf?raw=true) - poster at the Gordon Research Conference on *Biological Mechanisms in Evolution*, Stonehill College, Easton, MA, USA, June 2-6, 2013.

*   [**Evolution and mutation in stressful times**](https://speakerdeck.com/yoavram/bvlvtsyh-vmvttsyh-b-tvt-qh) - an oral presentation, part of the Evolution Series in Tel-Aviv University's Botanical Gardens, May 16, 2013.

*   [**Evolutionary Causes and Consequences of Stress-Induced Hypermutation**](http://dx.doi.org/10.6084/m9.figshare.96049) - oral presentation at *The 1st Graduate Students' Conference in Genetics, Genomics and Evolution*, Ben-Gurion University of the Negev, September 23, 2012. DOI: 10.6084/m9.figshare.96049

*   [**The Evolution of Stress-Induced Mutagenesis in Finite and Infinite Populations**](http://dx.doi.org/10.6084/m9.figshare.96049) - oral presentation at *PopGroup 45* in Nottingham, UK, January, 2012. DOI: 10.6084/m9.figshare.95939.

*   [**Rise and Fall of Mutator Bacteria**](http://dx.doi.org/10.6084/m9.figshare.95940) - seminar presentation at the *BioMath Student Journal Club*, Tel-Aviv University, May, 2011. DOI: 10.6084/m9.figshare.95940.

*   [**The Evolution of Stress-Induced Hypermutation**](http://f1000.com/posters/browse/summary/2211) - poster at ESEB 2011 in Tubingen, Germany, August, 2011.

*   **The Evolution of Stress-Induced Hypermutation** - poster at SMBE 2010 in Lyon, France, July, 2010.

